{"tid":759784,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖有片】男人愛高達 竟然有女仔好明白？","createTime":"2018-07-29T03:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T01:05:32.000Z","uid":81687,"like":145,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"24d308c01d38c65c518bcade647b38c17c30ae5e","tid":759784,"uid":81687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:12:35.000Z","msg":"有智者講過：「男人愛高達，女人唔明白」。趁住動漫節，我哋嚟到旺角模型聖地YM Studio，搵嚟兩位鍾意ACG文化嘅看板娘Newtype Girl，驗證吓呢句說話到底有幾成係真。<br />\n<br />\nGrace喺YM Studio做咗一年半，鍾意Cosplay、畫畫嘅佢受到一班模型高手嘅薰陶之下，開始學習砌模型，由機娘砌到去MG高達模型，打磨噴油全部做足。佢話身邊朋友第一次聽到佢砌模型都有啲驚訝，但佢就覺得點解女仔唔可以鍾意高達、鍾意模型，甚至可以同男朋友或者老公有共同話題，「傾吓點上色、上咩色，不過可能傾傾吓會嗌交。」<br />\n身高1.6米嘅160亦都喺YM Studio做咗一年，鍾意唱歌跳舞嘅佢性格有啲坐唔定，但原來亦都會砌吓模型，或者係幫啲Boardgame棋上色。佢話女仔砌模型其實就同男仔化妝一樣，根本唔應該去歧視，「何況宜家模型有好多唔同種類，好多女仔都個砌一啲可愛啲嘅。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180729/58489598\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180729%2F58489598&d=EiDfJdQdG%2FZi7HAVwIfDtAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=0f076542\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180729%2F58489598&h=ad241f63\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180729/58489598</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KSVSXNR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKSVSXNR.jpg&h=b94cd670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8JhSDhY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8JhSDhY.png&h=0d4687c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/P58A8hR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FP58A8hR.png&h=54b8e129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YG6hnlN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYG6hnlN.png&h=f654368d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解我遇唔到宅女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c7551a1e7cf25310af4a1a4ea034b1fcf92469","tid":759784,"uid":147367,"like":117,"dislike":7,"score":110,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:20:25.000Z","msg":"其實個女朋友都會砌先係悲哀<br />\n唯一可以自己話事既野都無埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我要一個唔阻止我砌已經夠"},{"pid":"d829c631c029a301a4906dc4f54981ba762ceb2d","tid":759784,"uid":98507,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:22:16.000Z","msg":"我細個砌都冇剪水口..."},{"pid":"64ccbbd7be8cdba5b9268c980d027fff792b631d","tid":759784,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:22:44.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"6d6a694df72d406f9093ba4a491db33efe9b978b","tid":759784,"uid":8307,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:24:01.000Z","msg":"個老細有冇食過個兩條女"},{"pid":"907e17dbcb29c9a5e9a66cceed666cb26809864f","tid":759784,"uid":81687,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"d829c631c029a301a4906dc4f54981ba762ceb2d","tid":759784,"uid":98507,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:22:16.000Z","msg":"我細個砌都冇剪水口..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:24:50.000Z","msg":"我指甲鉗..."},{"pid":"830f675bef22c2a5215afebce23b5772c1273374","tid":759784,"uid":81687,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"6d6a694df72d406f9093ba4a491db33efe9b978b","tid":759784,"uid":8307,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:24:01.000Z","msg":"個老細有冇食過個兩條女"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾十蚊時薪個鐘點食"},{"pid":"0fae75d755e9da5f74f0554837a2209c268850aa","tid":759784,"uid":190885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:26:43.000Z","msg":"好想砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\